These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, romance, fantasy
3 different pets are kept: turtle, chinchilla, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the owner of the chinchilla##7
2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
3. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | romance | disaster |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | goldfish     | turtle  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, blues, soul
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, roller, jet-ski
1. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere between the fan of soul and the person driving the roller##7
3. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | blues | hip-hop | soul |
| Transport     | roller       | jet-ski     | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, sprite
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, van, skateboard
1. the person driving the van is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person driving the tram##7
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | cola | sprite  |
| Transport   | skateboard  | van  | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, nurse, musician
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, satire, epic
1. the electrician is somewhere between the person watching epic movies and the nurse##7
2. the person watching satire movies is not the electrician##6
3. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | nurse | electrician | musician     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire    | fantasy          | epic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, soul, house
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, subway, bike
1. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the fan of soul##7
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the fan of house##1
3. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | house     | soul   |
| Transport     | bike | subway | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, soul
There are 3 different nationalities: german, spanish, malaysian
1. the german is on the left or right of the spanish##3
2. the spanish is somewhere to the left of the german##5
3. the fan of indie is on the right of the malaysian##1
4. the fan of indie is somewhere between the malaysian and the fan of dubstep##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | indie     | dubstep     |
| Nationality   | malaysian | spanish | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: fish, rabbit, frog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, biathlon, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the person who's sport is volleyball##7
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | frog       | rabbit      | fish       |
| Sport   | volleyball | water-polo | biathlon |

