2. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the dancer##7
3. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | designer | accountant  | dancer |
| Movie-Genre   | spy      | superhero | romance      |

