.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, drawing, singing
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, firefighter, mechanic
1. the mechanic is not the person who's hobby is singing##6
2. the firefighter is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the scientist is somewhere between the firefighter and the person who's hobby is drawing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | drawing | singing | camping   |
| Job     | mechanic    | scientist  | firefighter |

