.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, lemonade
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, snowboarding, sailing
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person who's sport is snowboarding##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | water   | lemonade    | soy-milk |
| Sport      | sailing | handball | snowboarding |

