.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, card-games, skydiving
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, colombian, chinese
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere between the colombian and the polish##7
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the polish is not the person who's hobby is skydiving##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | skydiving | video-games | card-games |
| Nationality   | colombian    | chinese    | polish         |

