.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, cherry, pear
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, western, adventure
1. the person watching western movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching animation movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person eating garlic##7
3. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food          | garlic  | pear       | cherry     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | animation | western |

