.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, 7up
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, reggae, salsa
1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the fan of pop and the fan of salsa##7
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the fan of reggae is somewhere between the fan of pop and the person drinking juice##7
4. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
| Beverage      | milk     | 7up | juice |
| Music-Genre   | pop | reggae    | salsa |

