.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-14::.
There 3 different types of food: mango, grapes, corn
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, taxi, quad-bike
1. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
2. the person driving the quad-bike is the person eating grapes##1
3. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person eating mango##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food        | grapes | corn | mango |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | taxi       | motorbike      |

