.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-16::.
There 3 different types of food: lime, cauliflower, kiwi
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, brazilian, mexican
1. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person eating kiwi##5
2. the person eating kiwi is the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere between the mexican and the japanese##7
4. the japanese is the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | kiwi | cauliflower     | lime   |
| Nationality   | mexican   | brazilian | japanese |

