.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, juice
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, journalist, designer
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the doctor##1
2. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the journalist##7
3. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the journalist##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate      | juice     | milk |
| Job        | designer | doctor | journalist    |

 